# Drop your annotator help videos here.
# Expected filenames (MP4 or WebM, autoplay loop, ~10-30s each):
#
#   01-my-tasks.mp4       — stat cards, task table, Start/Continue button
#   02-notifications.mp4  — bell icon with badge → notifications panel
#   03-layout.png         — full annotation view: waveform + accordion + editor panel
#   04-waveform.mp4       — play/pause, seek, zoom, speed, click-drag to add segment
#   05-speaker.mp4        — select segment → speaker label → gender → save
#   06-transcription.mp4  — click transcription segment → edit text → notes → save
#   07-emotions.mp4       — emotion checkboxes → add Other → ambiguous → save → badges
#   08-complete.mp4       — Mark Complete button → confirmation → auto-lock warning
#   09-remarks.mp4        — remarks box → type message → submit
#   10-shortcuts.mp4      — Space / S / N keys and the ? shortcuts panel
